Uses of Package
org.jcvi.jillion.experimental.align

  • Packages that use org.jcvi.jillion.experimental.align 
    Package Description
    org.jcvi.jillion.experimental.align  
  • Classes in org.jcvi.jillion.experimental.align used by org.jcvi.jillion.experimental.align 
    Class and Description
    AlnFileWriter
    AlnFileWriter can write aln encoded alignment files like those produced by Clustal.
    AlnFileWriter.AlnFileWriterBuilder
    AlnFileWriterBuilder is a Builder that can create new AlnFileWriter instances.
    AlnGroupVisitor 
    AlnGroupVisitor.ConservationInfo
    ConservationInfo contains information about how each column (slice) in a group block match.
    AlnParser 
    AlnVisitor
    AlnVisitor is a visitor interface to visit aln formatted data like that produced by multiple sequence alignment programs such as ClustalW.
    AlnVisitor.AlnVisitorCallback
    AlnVisitorCallback is a callback mechanism for the AlnVisitor instance to communicate with the parser that is parsing the aln data.
    AlnVisitor.AlnVisitorCallback.AlnVisitorMemento
    AlnVisitorMemento is a marker interface that AlnParser instances can use to "rewind" back to the position in its aln file in order to revisit portions of the aln file.
    AlnWriter
    AlnWriter can write aln encoded alignment files like those produced by Clustal.
